---
title: Plant-Based Ground Protein Souvlaki-Inspired Burgers with Zesty Potatoes
description: All of your favourite Greek-style flavours – plant-based ground protein, Mediterranean spices, fresh tomato salad and creamy feta mayo – are stacked between toasted brioche buns! The result is simple, convenient and delicious.
